    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {className: a3; text-indent: 48px;}\n.html-preview .a4 {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a5 {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .ConsPlusNonformat {font-family: 'Courier New'; font-size: 10pt;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 310.13850415512px;\">\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 326.16066481994px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">Иқтисодий ишлар бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#2}Ариза берилган иқтисодий суд номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\"> судига</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 310.13850415512px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 326.16066481994px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#6}Ариза берувчи юридик шахснинг номи ва ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 310.13850415512px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 326.16066481994px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">Манзил: </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#5}Ариза берувчи юридик шахснинг юридик манзили</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Талабларнинг бир қисмини бошқа иш юритувига ажратиш тўғрисида</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Иқтисодий ишлар бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#2}Ариза берилган иқтисодий суд номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> суди томонидан даъвогар </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#8}Иш бўйича даъвогарнинг номи ва ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">нинг жавобгар </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#9}Иш бўйича жавобгарнинг номи ва ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">га нисбатан </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#10}Даъво ариза мазмуни</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> тўғрисидаги даъво аризаси юзасидан юритилаётган иқтисодий иш кўриб чиқилмоқда. Иш тўлиқ, холисона ва ҳар томонлама кўриб чиқилиши, ишни кўриб чиқиш учун сарфланадиган вақтни қисқартириш мақсадида даъво талабларининг </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#11}Даъво аризанинг бошқа иш юритувига ажратилиши сўралаётган даъво талаблари (қисми)</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> қисмини алоҳида иш юритувига ажратиш мақсадга мувофиқ деб ҳисоблайман. </span></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси Иқтисодий процессуал Кодексининг 159-моддасига кўра, а</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">гар суд талабларни ажратиб кўришни мақсадга мувофиқ деб топса, у бир ёки бир нечта бирлаштирилган талабни алоҳида иш юритишга ажратишга ҳақли.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 7.5pt; text-indent: 56.733333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">Талабларнинг бир қисмини алоҳида иш юритишга ажратишга ишни кўриш якуни бўйича суд ҳужжати қабул қилингунига қадар ёки уни қабул қилиш билан бир вақтда йўл қўйилади. Талабларнинг қисмини алоҳида иш юритишга ажратиш тўғрисида ажрим чиқарилади. Ажратилган талаб бўйича ишни кўриш муддати ажрим чиқарилган кундан бошлаб ҳисобланади.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси Иқтисодий процессуал Кодексининг <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>159, 163-моддаларига асосан,</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">СЎРАЙМАН:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Мазкур иқтисодий иш бўйича даъво талабининг </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#11}Даъво аризанинг бошқа иш юритувига ажратилиши сўралаётган даъво талаблари (қисми)</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> қисмини бошқа (алоҳида) иш юритувига ажратишингизни.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">Илова: </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#12}Аризага илова қилинаётган ҳужжатлар номи</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 18.933333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#6}Ариза берувчи юридик шахснинг номи ва ташкилий ҳуқуқий шакли</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-style: italic;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#3}Ариза берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
